---
title: Double Tex-Mex Pulled Pork & Rice Bowl with Slaw & Herby Mayo
description: Discover classic Tex-Mex flavours with this aromatic rice bowl, piled with saucy pulled pork, tender veggies and zingy slaw. Top it
off with a some herby mayo and you’ve got a dinnertime hit!
